{"tid":1597502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足請繼續大大力屌612","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:55:14.000Z","uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d65f9d1dc6eb00625007c48938bea8bae86a017","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"因爲<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍屍</span>睇得好開心啊DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n從頭到尾，飯民同本土勇武嘅政治理念同行動方法都唔係100%接軌。你要612大大聲大大力支持前線買gear同叫國難幫人打官司有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n612係要監察，但唔係要佢收皮，令到有需要612幫嘅手足搵唔到人幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實612俾大家喪屌後，都用好多方法向大家交代。大家可唔可以唔好再問點解保釋金係借啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭101: 敵人的敵人，就是自己的朋友</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醒下啦LLM<br />\n從事抗爭，你要同你嘅朋友搵到最大公約數，團結最大最嘅力量，一齊打到港共政權。<br />\n就算你同佢理念唔係exact7ly一樣，但只要612都係對抗緊港共政權，我真係睇唔到同612搞個對立面有乜好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你有本事開個新嘅前線基金，只支援前線買gear，提供安家費，又可以係現有暴政法律底下繼續運作，唔俾暴政凍結你筆錢，唔該快啲搞，前線需要你。但收612皮唔會幫到你達到目標。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。 不割席，不分化，不篤灰。<br />\n只要大家嘅目標仍然係港共政權，要做嘅就係互相提點優化，而唔係打個你死我活。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 屌音響嘅手足可以了解下民陣搞遊行，俾其他機構遊行期間籌錢嘅機制。<br />\nP.S. 2 民陣=/=612<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.S.3 P牌預咗俾人屌，但真係希望大家將力量對準。"},{"pid":"3f1a400924cd609d9532e2827d26f12b21cb42fc","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"17116c185930647991bd35992fb18470d735701e","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"07be2f6a493cc3af0904640ed8ba30ae1b43a87a","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"68e166bd088aa60a0310dab5904f4829e727dc20","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"fa3bacc54277301a7f5f92f05b1d9c75d0134b9d","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"90cdf3603280e0ce02779226cb35d60449450540","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:39:35.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"cf6813cad930a0b386c277904f3ead5280db4ffa","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"6f0d1da5143cc9d2a324e250138112f5cdae4e00","tid":1597502,"uid":287863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"8/10"}]}